{"tid":2117092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇黃西裝店介紹？","createTime":"2020-07-20T14:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T10:27:16.000Z","uid":110984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5e916d58dd7c09b9a659bbcdc338245c119b83c1","tid":2117092,"uid":110984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"今日諗住叫老竇帶我去做西裝<br />\n不嬲都知佢藍㗎喇不過做西裝呢啲嘢佢應該多經驗過我咁我就問佢啦諗住求其做一件算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢帶咗我去間野叫意x洋服<br />\n我諗住上網睇吓佢係咪黃先俾錢幫襯<br />\n點知上網一睇佢係用曾志偉做代言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OE3TjCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOE3TjCD.jpg&h=c5ecf859&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7d78v0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7d78v0.png&h=14ae1be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問吓大家有冇啲咩黃嘅西裝店介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一蚊都唔想俾啲仆街藍店賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：budget $5000左右"},{"pid":"dcc78ca5fbcc764f6a1801f1a80aa393ea494694","tid":2117092,"uid":27482,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"Zuitable"},{"pid":"c55a662e1b7546da7de9900fc33cc0689c6679ff","tid":2117092,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcc78ca5fbcc764f6a1801f1a80aa393ea494694","tid":2117092,"uid":27482,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"Zuitable"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9eb040d093b8b59c513284edc57400f1446b9fa1","tid":2117092,"uid":135798,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VdAiL_G4oLY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVdAiL_G4oLY&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=f7e90d2e\